Detailed Description

Purpose: DS Endpoint-side Task control block

Members: dsusdldcb - DL package control block for logging dsusdwaiter - Waiter structure used by the DS Endpoint task for timing during startup and for blocking during waiting for messages from the modem dsbufpool - MM pool structure. Blocks in this pool are used to store incoming data packets from the modem for EP side dsrxpktsdropped - number of rx packets dropped

Notes: none
